This is a client server multi-threat hangman game.
First start server. You can enter a port number or use default port if left empty.
The port will be used for socket communication
When server is ready you can check it from java console, you can start client
If a different port is defined enter it or leave empty for default port.
If server is running localhost you can leave ip empty again otherwise enter server ip.
For each connected client there will be a threat.
when you start the game client will get the word from server and each win will be counted for 1 point for total score.
At most 10 clients can connect at the same time which is set in the server part.